# Component Patterns

## Section Components

### Standard Section Structure
```tsx
<section className="py-28 px-14 bg-white">
  <div className="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto">
    <SectionHeader label="LABEL" headline="Headline" />
    {/* Content */}
  </div>
</section>
```

### Split-Screen Pattern
```tsx
<section className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 min-h-[600px]">
  <div className="p-20 flex flex-col justify-center bg-cream">
    {/* Content */}
  </div>
  <div className="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-200 to-gray-300">
    {/* Visual placeholder */}
  </div>
</section>
```

## Animation Wrapper
Always wrap animated elements with Framer Motion:
```tsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
  whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.6 }}
  viewport={{ once: true }}
>
  {children}
</motion.div>
```

## Image Placeholders
Never use real image URLs. Use this pattern:
```tsx
<div className="h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-200 to-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center">
  <span className="text-gray-500 text-sm px-4 py-2 bg-black/60 text-white rounded-md">
    [Description of intended image]
  </span>
</div>
```

## Button Variants
- Primary (green): `bg-green hover:bg-green-dark text-white`
- Secondary (dark): `bg-dark hover:bg-gray-800 text-white`
- Outline: `border-2 border-gray-300 hover:border-dark text-dark`
- White (on dark): `bg-white text-dark hover:bg-gray-100`

